Company Profile
Hubeiyichang Transportation Group Co., Ltd. engages in the passenger transport services. It covers road passenger transport, water passenger transport, and bus terminal and ferry terminal station services. It provides road and water transit within the same traffic hub. The company also engages in the automobile dealership and maintenance industry. It mainly sales branded series car such as Dongfeng Nissan, Fengshen, Citroen, Peugeot, and Shanghai Volkswagen. The company was founded on August 10, 1998 and is headquartered in Yichang, China
