Summary for Hubeiyichang Transportation Group Co.,Ltd.
HUBEIYICHANG TRANSPORTATION GROUP CO., LTD. is principally engaged in the provision of passenger transportation services and the distribution of automobiles. The Company operates its businesses primarily through passenger transportation services, which include road passenger transportation, water passenger transportation, vehicle passenger station services and port services, among others, such as shuttle bus passenger transportation, traveller transportation, chartered bus transportation, water passenger transportation, agent ship services, ship stopping and station services, as well as automobile distribution and maintenance services, which involve in the distribution of NISSAN, CITROEN, AEOLUS and PEUGEOT automobiles. As of December 31, 2010, the Company operated four ports and six automobile 4S shops (sale, survey, spare parts, services). The Company operates its businesses primarily in Yichang and Enshi, Hubei province, China.


